{"tid":682103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"徒手爬4層樓救男童 巴黎新移民獲馬克龍安排入籍法國","createTime":"2018-05-28T14:45:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T03:04:38.000Z","uid":29627,"like":322,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"d39528d4054c0c2f69f9474b459325c30f5122cb","tid":682103,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:45:03.000Z","msg":"徒手爬4層樓救男童 巴黎新移民獲馬克龍安排入籍法國 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180528/large/1527511318_bb8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180528%2Flarge%2F1527511318_bb8d.jpg&h=ade9e6a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法國巴黎一名小孩懸吊在4樓露台極為危險，幸得一位新移民男子奮勇爬上露台，將他救回安全地方，<span style=\"color: red;\">這位英雄周一更獲總統馬克龍安排在愛麗舍宮接見，將特准入籍法國，並安排受訓當消防員。</span><br />\n<br />\n事發於周六下午，影片拍到一名小孩在露台懸吊，有人在上層伸手拉着他，一名男子則以非凡的身手，只用了20多秒，就由地下經露台一層一層爬到四樓，再一手抽起小孩，將他帶回平地，圍觀者都不禁鼓掌喝采。<br />\n<br />\n救人的22歲男子為來自馬里的賈薩瑪（Mamoudou Gassama），他幾個月前才移居巴黎，說道︰「我這樣做因為他是個小孩&hellip;&hellip;就爬上去，感謝神，我能救到他。」<br />\n<br />\n巴黎市長伊達戈還親自致電答謝他，讚揚他為「第18區的蜘蛛俠」，並在Twitter公開讚揚他︰「他的英勇行為是所有市民的典範，巴黎會他支援，讓他適應在法國的生活。」總統馬克龍周一更邀請他到愛麗舍宮，親自向他道謝。<br />\n<br />\n當地傳媒指，事發前男童家人都不在家，消息指男童母親當時不在巴黎，男童爸爸則因為懷疑獨留兒童在家而被警方問話。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180528/58246137\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180528%2F58246137&d=jlRBYHib%2BaS0QAhTTreFxzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=aa2f38a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180528%2F58246137&h=541740d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180528/58246137</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc5b9e6b084dfb3c9ff16b6e4ed03230b83a88f3","tid":682103,"uid":113092,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:47:28.000Z","msg":"真英雄"},{"pid":"57e7e0361450b460beacbee044778b703553c22c","tid":682103,"uid":27356,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:47:48.000Z","msg":"痴撚線廿秒爬咗上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f84246136daf89c46b64064327b95e2a832429","tid":682103,"uid":41204,"like":41,"dislike":313,"score":-272,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:55:28.000Z","msg":"淨係擔心以後有人刻意製造意外來博入籍"},{"pid":"f6faa3f5c3a22b12ff7f3be0670de50b1ed52452","tid":682103,"uid":75050,"like":134,"dislike":1,"score":133,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:59:23.000Z","msg":"入咩消防隊，入兄弟會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb65e0427c33aaad16865a588a26c8835e7f0f38","tid":682103,"uid":61675,"like":65,"dislike":5,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T15:02:38.000Z","msg":"呢個力架真心勁"},{"pid":"85c058e14f46625c44cdd1f43bebc6c60a535b2d","tid":682103,"uid":32527,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"quote":{"pid":"fb65e0427c33aaad16865a588a26c8835e7f0f38","tid":682103,"uid":61675,"like":65,"dislike":5,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T15:02:38.000Z","msg":"呢個力架真心勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T15:04:52.000Z","msg":"黑豹"},{"pid":"0a7ff08d2bf25fd58c8e30fc58fc1ed70aa560c9","tid":682103,"uid":32527,"like":106,"dislike":23,"score":83,"quote":{"pid":"57e7e0361450b460beacbee044778b703553c22c","tid":682103,"uid":27356,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T14:47:48.000Z","msg":"痴撚線廿秒爬咗上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T15:05:18.000Z","msg":"老爆爬得多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24704979ecd2157820ba0fe31dd40a44dc66e50d","tid":682103,"uid":78349,"like":232,"dislike":9,"score":223,"quote":{"pid":"28f84246136daf89c46b64064327b95e2a83